# ─── AI character chat (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# The app builds and runs fine WITHOUT these. When unset, the chat unlocks on
# win but the character politely explains that live chat isn't configured.
#
# Get a free key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Model id for the Gemini generateContent REST API. Defaults to gemini-1.5-flash.
GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-1.5-flash

# Optional: switch the active LLM provider (default "gemini"). Additional
# providers are registered in src/lib/llm.ts.
# LLM_PROVIDER=gemini
